# Phase 3 — Speech Processing

## Objectives

Convert telecall recordings into text transcripts.

### Tasks

- Implement audio upload
- Integrate Whisper speech recognition
- Generate transcripts

### Example Implementation

```python
import whisper

model = whisper.load_model("base")
result = model.transcribe("call_audio.wav")

print(result["text"])
````

