# 3. Datasets and AI Models

Three types of datasets are required.

| Dataset Type       | Purpose                        |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------ |
| Speech datasets    | Speech recognition testing     |
| Sentiment datasets | Emotion detection              |
| Fraud datasets     | Suspicious behaviour detection |

---

# Speech Datasets

## Mozilla Common Voice

Large open speech dataset for speech recognition.

---

## Switchboard Dataset

Telephone conversation dataset.

---

## CallHome Dataset

Real telephone conversations.

---

# Sentiment Analysis Datasets

## GoEmotions Dataset

Developed by Google.

Features:

* 27 emotion categories
* High-quality labelled data

---

## Sentiment140

Large sentiment dataset from Twitter.

---

# Fraud Detection Datasets

## ScamCall Dataset

Contains scam phone conversation transcripts.

---

## Jigsaw Toxic Comment Dataset

Dataset for detecting abusive communication.

---

